I just read the transcripts, that's all.

01:55:28.893 --> 01:55:31.020
What do you wanna know, Howard?

01:55:31.195 --> 01:55:33.356
Was I screwing Artie Shaw last night?

01:55:33.531 --> 01:55:36.227
